item.title: My Journey Of Building Robots
item.description: I am 14 years old and I have been coding and building robots since I was 9 years old. I have built 5 robots. My motivation to be a part of GDG Devfest is to be able to encourage other kids especially girls that technology is fun and its good to be able to use technology for human benefit.
